Package: weblatetools
Title: Download, Edit, and Upload Weblate Translation Files
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Simon",
           family = "Kaiser",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sim.kai@bluewin.ch")
Description: This package provides functions to (1) get a list of components for
     a given Weblate project, and (2) download translation files
    for such a list of components from a Weblate project, edit them 
    (search/replace & filter unwanted terms) and then reupload them to matching 
    components in the same or a different Weblate project.
